OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FA wholesale drug dealer who was found
OL,7,Fwith numerous firearms including sawn-
OL,8,Foff shotguns as well as cocaine and
OL,9,Fattempted to flee from officers who
OL,10,Fdiscovered his stash in a shipping
OL,11,Fcontainer has been jailed.
OL,13,FDavid Smith, 35, was arrested
OL,14,Ffollowing a raid on his shipping
OL,15,Fcontainer in Tonypandy on January 19.
OL,17,FWhen police arrived at the container a
OL,18,Fstolen Ford EcoSport was seen trying
OL,19,Fto escape from an embankment but
OL,20,Frolled backwards.
