OL,6,FA sentencing hearing at Merthyr Tydfil
OL,7,FCrown Court heard the driver was Coran
OL,8,FDavies, 22, who was found in
OL,9,Fpossession of four keys which unlocked
OL,10,Fpadlocks on the shipping container
OL,11,Fwhile he also had cash and 28g of
OL,12,Fcannabis.
OL,14,FWhen police searched the shipping
OL,15,Fcontainer in Wern Street, Clydach
OL,16,FVale, they discovered a carrier bag
OL,17,Fcontaining pink rocks.
