OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FThis was found to be metonitazene ` a
OL,7,Fsynthetic opioid described by
OL,8,Fprosecutor John Ryan as being "a 100
OL,9,Ftimes more potent than diamorphine".
OL,11,FThe drug was said to have originated
OL,12,Fin China and was sold as "fake heroin"
OL,13,Fwhich had a high risk of users
OL,14,Foverdosing.
OL,16,FAlso found in the container was a
OL,17,Fsignificant amount of cutting agents,
OL,18,Fmore than 6kg of cannabis trimmings, a
OL,19,Fhydraulic press, and digital scales
OL,20,Fcontaining traces of various drugs.
