OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FIt was discovered that Smith had fled
OL,7,Ffrom the area in a Range Rover Sport.
OL,8,FHe was seen riding as a passenger in a
OL,9,Fwhite car which was stopped by the
OL,10,Fpolice. When searched he was found
OL,11,Fwith cash, a Range Rover key, and a
OL,12,Fbalaclava.
OL,14,FThe Range Rover Sport was discovered
OL,15,Fnearby and contained an ID card in
OL,16,FSmith's name, cash, two packages of
OL,17,Fcocaine weighting 55.4g and 41.9g
OL,18,Frespectively, a passport, car keys,
OL,19,Fand a receipt in his name.
