OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FSmith, of Francis Street, Clydach
OL,7,FVale, later pleaded guilty to two
OL,8,Fcounts of possessing a prohibited
OL,9,Ffirearm, possessing a disguised
OL,10,Ffirearm, possessing a prohibited
OL,11,Fweapon, possession with intent to
OL,12,Fsupply Class A and B drugs, and
OL,13,Fpossession of a psychoactive substance
OL,14,Fwith intent to supply.
OL,16,FThe court heard he has 14 previous
OL,17,Fconvictions including possession of a
OL,18,Ffirearm with intent to endanger life,
OL,19,Ffor which he received a five-year
OL,20,Fprison sentence, and conspiracy to
OL,21,Fsupply controlled drugs of Class B.
