OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FDavies, of High Street, Clydach Vale,
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to possession with
OL,8,Fintent to supply a psychoactive
OL,9,Fsubstance, possession with intent to
OL,10,Fsupply Class B drugs, and handling
OL,11,Fstolen goods. The court heard he has
OL,12,Flimited previous convictions including
OL,13,Fpossession of cannabis and possession
OL,14,Fof an offensive weapon.
OL,16,FIn mitigation for Smith barrister
OL,17,FSteven Donoghue said his client had
OL,18,Fbeen helping the authorities since his
OL,19,Farrest and had been given enhanced
OL,20,Fprison status.
