OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FHe said the defendant, who has a seven-
OL,7,Fyear-old daughter, wished to put his
OL,8,Fcriminal behaviour behind him and live
OL,9,Fa more stable and law-abiding life.
OL,11,FIn mitigation for Davies barrister
OL,12,FHashim Salmman said there was a
OL,13,Frealistic prospect of rehabilitation
OL,14,Fin his client's case and was in a
OL,15,Fdifferent position to his co-defendant.
OL,17,FHe said the defendant faced challenges
OL,18,Fat school but had obtained employment
OL,19,Fin the construction industry though he
OL,20,Fwas misusing cannabis and was
OL,21,Fsusceptible to being easily influenced.
