OL,3,CWholesale drug dealer jailed as police
OL,4,Cuncover guns, drugs, and cash
OL,6,FJudge Simon Mills said: "The two of
OL,7,Fyou were involved at different levels
OL,8,Fin street dealing and a wholesale drug
OL,9,Fdealing business.... You used a base
OL,10,Fto carry out business where drugs were
OL,11,Fadulterated, weighed, and prepared for
OL,12,Fonward supply."
OL,14,FThe judge told Smith the weapons were
OL,15,Fclearly designed to "protect" his drug
OL,16,Fdealing business. He added: "You knew
OL,17,Fvery well the risks of getting
OL,18,Finvolved in crime as serious as this."
